00:02:31.351 --> 00:02:32.854 position:44% line:89% align:start
King!

00:02:32.887 --> 00:02:33.855 position:21% line:83% align:start
Where are you hiding,
you silly boy?

00:02:33.888 --> 00:02:34.922 position:38% line:89% align:start
Oh, Nemo.

00:02:42.864 --> 00:02:45.833 position:19% line:89% align:start
Is Madame still asleep?

00:02:45.867 --> 00:02:47.635 position:33% line:89% align:start
You knew it.

00:02:47.669 --> 00:02:51.706 position:7% line:83% align:start
I can't remember the last time
she woke up at a decent hour.

00:02:51.739 --> 00:02:55.275 position:7% line:83% align:start
If you stayed up half the night
fantasizing about Captain Nemo,

00:02:55.308 --> 00:02:56.644 position:21% line:89% align:start
you'd sleep late too.

00:02:56.678 --> 00:02:59.781 position:13% line:83% align:start
What could she possibly see
in a middle-aged guy

00:02:59.814 --> 00:03:01.481 position:19% line:89% align:start
who dresses like that?

00:03:01.516 --> 00:03:03.450 position:35% line:89% align:start
Hey, Jean.

00:03:03.483 --> 00:03:05.887 position:16% line:83% align:start
You look like the canary
that got eaten by the cat.

00:03:05.920 --> 00:03:07.454 position:33% line:89% align:start
Huh? Uh-hmm.

00:03:07.487 --> 00:03:09.256 position:10% line:89% align:start
Are you worried about Nadia?

00:03:09.289 --> 00:03:10.658 position:41% line:89% align:start
Uh-huh.

00:03:10.692 --> 00:03:12.694 position:19% line:89% align:start
I can't figure her out.

00:03:12.727 --> 00:03:15.663 position:24% line:83% align:start
Why did our hunting
bother her so much?

00:03:15.697 --> 00:03:18.231 position:38% line:83% align:start
Why can't
she talk to anyone now?

00:03:18.265 --> 00:03:20.702 position:33% line:83% align:start
I wish girls
came with instructions.

00:03:20.735 --> 00:03:22.503 position:10% line:89% align:start
Well, you know what they say,

00:03:22.537 --> 00:03:26.541 position:19% line:83% align:start
a woman's heart is like
the mystery of the universe.

00:03:26.574 --> 00:03:29.309 position:19% line:83% align:start
You'll never understand
anything they do.

00:03:29.342 --> 00:03:31.679 position:30% line:83% align:start
Well, it sounds
very usual of Nadia.

00:03:31.713 --> 00:03:34.515 position:5% line:89% align:start
You don't understand her either?

00:03:34.549 --> 00:03:37.785 position:27% line:83% align:start
You've witnessed
Grandis, haven't you?

00:03:37.819 --> 00:03:39.654 position:21% line:89% align:start
I see what you mean.

00:03:39.687 --> 00:03:42.724 position:5% line:83% align:start
Do you think Nadia wants to live
all by herself?

00:03:42.757 --> 00:03:43.991 position:30% line:89% align:start
Maybe she does.

00:03:44.025 --> 00:03:46.661 position:10% line:83% align:start
But humans were not designed
to live alone

00:03:46.694 --> 00:03:50.330 position:7% line:83% align:start
and it only brings them misery
when they try.

00:03:50.363 --> 00:03:53.668 position:19% line:83% align:start
Nadia will realize this
before too long.

00:03:53.701 --> 00:03:55.302 position:16% line:89% align:start
Are you sure about that?

00:03:55.335 --> 00:03:57.605 position:21% line:89% align:start
You can count on it.

00:03:57.638 --> 00:04:00.307 position:13% line:83% align:start
So it's time for breakfast.
Why don't you fetch them?

00:04:00.340 --> 00:04:01.809 position:35% line:89% align:start
Good idea.

00:04:01.843 --> 00:04:04.679 position:27% line:89% align:start
