00:04:34.976 --> 00:04:36.010 position:30% line:89% align:start
Did you eat it?

00:04:36.043 --> 00:04:37.845 position:30% line:89% align:start
Did I eat what?

00:04:37.879 --> 00:04:40.447 position:13% line:83% align:start
