maybe you're the one

00:05:13.915 --> 00:05:14.916 position:10% line:89% align:start
who hasn't tried hard enough.

00:05:14.949 --> 00:05:16.383 position:16% line:89% align:start
[Nadia] What did you say?

00:05:16.416 --> 00:05:18.786 position:27% line:83% align:start
Uh, you're having
another lovers' spat?

00:05:18.820 --> 00:05:20.320 position:30% line:83% align:start
