00:05:25.126 --> 00:05:27.427 position:24% line:83% align:start
[Jean] I don't see
what the big problem is, Nadia.

00:05:27.460 --> 00:05:28.896 position:19% line:89% align:start
[Nadia] It's so savage.

00:05:28.930 --> 00:05:31.632 position:10% line:83% align:start
