It's just good food.

00:05:31.666 --> 00:05:33.768 position:24% line:83% align:start
[Nadia] Animals are
our companions, not food.

00:05:33.801 --> 00:05:36.070 position:13% line:83% align:start
[Jean] But they become food
once you cook them.

00:05:36.103 --> 00:05:38.906 position:7% line:83% align:start
Don't even feel sorry for them
when you see what you've done?

00:05:38.940 --> 00:05:40.440 position:33% line:89% align:start
