00:05:40.473 --> 00:05:41.108 position:19% line:83% align:start
Because the only reason
they're dead

00:05:41.142 --> 00:05:43.077 position:16% line:89% align:start
is to serve your hunger.

00:05:43.110 --> 00:05:44.612 position:7% line:89% align:start
If there was a way to eat them

00:05:44.645 --> 00:05:46.013 position:21% line:83% align:start
without killing them,
then I would do it.

00:05:46.047 --> 00:05:48.115 position:19% line:83% align:start
Well, there's something
terribly wrong with you

00:05:48.149 --> 00:05:49.784 position:24% line:83% align:start
