kill animals

00:05:49.817 --> 00:05:51.484 position:30% line:83% align:start
without feeling
any pity for them.

00:05:51.519 --> 00:05:53.420 position:19% line:83% align:start
I felt kind of bad for
the baby deer

00:05:53.453 --> 00:05:55.089 position:5% line:89% align:start
