00:20:54.589 --> 00:20:56.289 position:41% line:89% align:start
Marie.

00:20:56.323 --> 00:20:58.325 position:27% line:89% align:start
Here, King. Huh?

00:21:01.328 --> 00:21:03.598 position:33% line:89% align:start
[King purrs]

00:21:03.631 --> 00:21:05.566 position:44% line:89% align:start
King.

00:21:05.600 --> 00:21:08.569 position:16% line:83% align:start
